ay）（IG@annehathaway）\"><figcaption>安妮夏菲維（Anne Hathaway）（IG@annehathaway）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250212/966301473472253952453701.jpeg/cUO_rhaCGa1xlme0RGnMZBLq8bYrLaTvDyT4cQ8k-HE\" alt=\"安妮夏菲維（Anne Hathaway）（IG@annehathaway）\"><figcaption>安妮夏菲維（Anne Hathaway）（IG@annehathaway）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250212/966301472591450112673280.jpeg/TOyDcDUkr2a-9SJpRMfh18o26ajnjGFFIczOFCHMzhQ\" alt=\"安妮夏菲維（Anne Hathaway）（IG@annehathaway）\"><figcaption>安妮夏菲維（Anne Hathaway）（IG@annehathaway）</figcaption></figure><p>延伸閱讀：</p><p>安海瑟薇徹底顛覆形象！控制慾藏危險魅力 舉手投足暗藏威脅</p><p>日本互動式神作「催眠麥克風」登台！製作人來台逛超商看1影片秒感動</p><p>【本文獲「聯合新聞網」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-30T09:15:00.062612+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1826,"images":31,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}